:''This page is a sortable list of every structure. For a guided, room-by-room tour of building your castle, see [[Castle Building]].''
This page lists every '''structure''' you can place in your castle — production stations, walls, floors, furniture, lighting and more. Structures are unlocked through the [[Journal]], by defeating [[V Blood Carriers]], or researched at the [[Research Desk]].

==All structures==
Every structure on the wiki, drawn automatically from each structure page's infobox. Click a column header to sort — by room to see what belongs together, or by name to find a specific station.
